INT. KITCHEN - DAY

MARA stands at the counter, slicing an apple with careful precision.

She glances at the clock.

MARA
We're going to be late.

DEREK
(from offscreen)
I'm looking for my keys!

MARA
They're on the hook. Where they always are.

Derek enters, flustered, holding his keys aloft.

DEREK
Found them.

MARA
Miracles happen.

They exit together.

INT. CAR - CONTINUOUS

Derek starts the engine. Mara buckles her seatbelt.

DEREK
Music?

MARA
Anything but that podcast.
